flowchart LR
    subgraph parse [lambda input css]
        A[Stylesheet text] --> B[CSS parser]
        B --> C[CssDeclaration values with specificity origin source order]
        C --> D[Selector match plus cascade]
        D --> E[StyleTree AVL keyed by CssPropertyId]
        E --> F[StyleNode winning_decl plus weak_list of losers]
    end
    subgraph radiant [radiant resolve]
        F --> G[dom_elem specified_style read only]
        G --> H[resolve_css_property switch]
        H --> I[Value resolvers length color var]
        I --> J[Computed props on view node]
    end
    J --> K[FontProp InlineProp BoundaryProp BlockProp FlexProp PositionProp]
    K --> L[Consumed by layout and renderer]
